    <note>Han(1) Yanzhi [667] Shizhong's [8050] son. His younger brother, Yanzhi(2) [3330], was Liangzhe yunpan for two terms starting in 1178 and 1180, Huaixi zongling in 1183, and Hubu shilang between 1183 and 1184. Another younger brother, Yangu [3331], was Hubu shilang from 1177 to 1178 when he was appointed Hubu shangshu. Zhang Xiaoxiang, WJ, 19.8b; Jiangxi TZ, 10.20b-21a; XNYL, 184.8a, 195.6b; Xianchun Linan zhi, 50.8a; Shengzheng, 55.1b 61.8a; SHY:ZG, 41.59b, 71.18a, 72.5b; SHY:SH, 56.57a, 58b, 59b, 60a, 62b; SS, 364.15a. CBD, 5, 4174.</note>
